With this menu entry, you can DIRECTLY EDIT THE TOR CONFIGURATION FILE. You find some helpful comments in the configuration file. Nevertheless, you should know what you are doing. If you are unsure, then contact us: anonym@torbox.ch

After changing the configuration, use the following commands in the editor:
CTRL-S to save the changes.
CTRL-X to exit the editor.

